beer.beer_description:
Mosaic/Idaho-7/Citra

What happens when you cross Bracket Brewing with Big Shed Brewing? They brew a big beer!

Ben flew up from Adelaide last month to brew a modern imperial IPA with Mike. Charlie stood in shock as he watched them throw the most expensive ingredients they could get their hands on into this brew and Big Spender was born.
